2.  While Unit 00 (Zerogoki) and Unit 02 (Nogoki) and the other EVA's were made by cloning Adam, Unit 01 (Shogoki) was actually made from Lilith, making it very special.  Eva's have souls in them to keep them stable.  Unit 01 has Yui in there, who disspeared during the first activation experiment.  That's why it protects Shinji.  Unit 02 has Asuka's mother, and Unit 00 has Dr. Agaki.  Dr Agaki commited suicide after killing Rei I. She jumped of the Magi housing.<br>
3.  Remember when we see the flashback of how Nerv was formed?  Gendo explains to Fuyutsuki that the Geofront wasn't excavated, it was already formed.  This is called Lillith's egg.  Lillith, officially the second angel, is the mother of all mankind.  She was found there when Seele looked for it, after they read about her in the dead sea scrolls.  They used the Lance of Longinus to keep her under control, so that the same thing as with Adam wouldn't happen.<br>
<br>
you have to see EVA multiple times to get it.  I'm not certain about a lot of things, but that seems to be clear to me.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/unaokochan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naoko Chan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hot Sexy B*tch <img src=http://contest.polykarbon.com/badge1.gif></span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/14/02 10:17:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1378.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://naokochan.xoasis.com/ayako02.gif width=60 height=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  N</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> They used the Lance of Longinus to keep her under control, so that the same thing as with Adam wouldn't happen<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
You have to remember one thing though.  Nerv never got back the spear of longinus until episode 12.  When Gendo Fuyutsuki went to the South Pole.  And what was on the carrier that they were riding on?  A very long something that was covered up (it can be argued that they went there to retrieve the spear).  And then at the end of episode 14, you see Rei in Unit 00 going down the corridor with the spear of longinus.  Supposedly going to Lilith and stab her with it (I'm assuming to keep her from regaining her complete form).  Then finally you see confirmation of this in episode 15.<br>
<br>
If they didn't have that spear for 15 years (I'm assuming that they used it against Adam in the south pole, where they had to retrive it in ep. 12), how did they keep Lilith under control from the formation of Nerv until episode 14?  (where Lilith gets stabbed for the first time)<br>
